  "text": "Throughput: Our experiment shows that Infnote's throughput can reach approximately 150,000 posts per second, running the Go version of the Infnote program on a 64-bit machine with an Intel Core i7 CPU @2.70GHz with 16GB RAM. The result could be further improved by deploying better hardware or optimizing the code. Bitcoin, which takes approximately ten minutes to confirm a block, achieves only 7 transactions per second maximum throughput [CITATION_1] .",
